"biometric_consent_title" = "Biometric Data Consent";
"biometric_consent_body" = "Processed Biometric Data\n\nThe following special category personal data will be processed as part of the identity verification process:\n• Your face image taken during the liveness test and the biometric photo on the chip of your identity card.\n\nPurpose of Processing\n\nThis data is used solely for biometric matching to verify that the identity card belongs to you.\n\nHow It Is Processed\n\nYour data is transmitted to our servers end-to-end encrypted (AES-256 + RSA-OAEP); the match is calculated only in the secure processing environment (AWS Nitro Enclave).\n\nNot Stored and Deleted\n\nYour biometric data is never recorded or stored. It is permanently deleted immediately after the match result is obtained. It is not shared with third parties.\n\nWithdrawal of Consent\n\nYou can withdraw this consent at any time. If you withdraw your consent, operations requiring biometric verification cannot be performed.";
"biometric_consent_text" = "Processed Biometric Data\n\nThe following special category personal data will be processed within the scope of the identity verification process:\n• Your facial image taken during the liveness test and the biometric photo on the chip of your identity card.\n\nPurpose of Processing\n\nThis data is used solely in biometric matching verification to confirm that the identity card belongs to you.\n\nHow It Is Processed\n\nYour data is transmitted to our servers end-to-end encrypted (AES-256 + RSA-OAEP); the matching calculation is performed only in a secure processing environment (AWS Nitro Enclave).\n\nNot Stored and Deleted\n\nYour biometric data is not recorded or stored in any way. It is permanently deleted immediately after the matching result is obtained. It is not shared with third parties.\n\nWithdrawal of Your Consent\n\nYou can withdraw this consent at any time. If you withdraw your consent, operations requiring biometric verification cannot be performed.";
